{"tid":2214600,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"螞蟻集團明日香港闖關 傳香港集資175億美元","createTime":"2020-09-23T11:04:43.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-23T12:57:33.000Z","uid":150305,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"8f8847802a2ecd9c997374edb82961168d5eabb0","tid":2214600,"uid":150305,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-23T11:04:43.000Z","msg":"【螞蟻IPO】螞蟻集團明日香港闖關 傳香港集資175億美元、不尋求基石投資者<br />\n（23/9）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://inews.hket.com/article/2748497/【螞蟻IPO】螞蟻集團明日香港闖關%20%20傳香港集資175億美元、不尋求基石投資者\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Finews.hket.com%2Farticle%2F2748497%2F%E3%80%90%E8%9E%9E%E8%9F%BBIPO%E3%80%91%E8%9E%9E%E8%9F%BB%E9%9B%86%E5%9C%98%E6%98%8E%E6%97%A5%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E9%97%96%E9%97%9C%2520%2520%E5%82%B3%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E9%9B%86%E8%B3%87175%E5%84%84%E7%BE%8E%E5%85%83%E3%80%81%E4%B8%8D%E5%B0%8B%E6%B1%82%E5%9F%BA%E7%9F%B3%E6%8A%95%E8%B3%87%E8%80%85&d=UZIDdMkqB5nEVwovtN1d9j%2FbAHlNv8jCBJNC2S%2BJHYY%3D&h=ce74c1db\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://inews.hket.com/article/2748497/【螞蟻IPO】螞蟻集團明日香港闖關%20%20傳香港集資175億美元、不尋求基石投資者</a>（第七版）?mtc=20023<br />\n<br />\n阿里巴巴\t（09988） 同系的螞蟻集團（前稱：螞蟻金服）中港上市倒數。據外電報道，螞蟻集團計劃於香港集資約175億美元（約1365億港元）。早前有傳螞蟻A+H上市集資提高至350億美元，意味螞蟻中港上市集資或各佔一半。同時螞蟻香港上市將不會尋求基石投資者參與，認為在沒有基石投資者的情況下亦可順利招股。知情人士稱，螞蟻傾向於邀請大型投資者參與上海IPO，從而緩和價格波動。<br />\n<br />\n⋯⋯⋯⋯<br />\n<br />\n外電消息指，螞蟻集團暫時計劃於內地國慶假期（10月1日至8日）後建簿，預計約10月底上市。<br />\n<br />\n⋯⋯⋯"},{"pid":"869ee8994b27aaf52cbcfb8386daf49ea3f80f18","tid":2214600,"uid":191588,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-23T11:06:40.000Z","msg":"買啦買啦。<br />\n正股驚西咩"},{"pid":"9715257bde8fd072d8075c1f8ade42df8dd888b4","tid":2214600,"uid":259901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-23T11:18:45.000Z","msg":"抽<br />\n抽完呢浸好走<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d30692593f89df5bbacc5a7d6de1206c23209056","tid":2214600,"uid":36724,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-23T12:49:19.000Z","msg":"會唔會係基金佬唔落，提早大冧市"},{"pid":"235f66482241ff73e371e869dc0421223ead9674","tid":2214600,"uid":180251,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-23T12:51:35.000Z","msg":"1人1手"},{"pid":"ad70e1228b4f52b7846835a06635018fe2cada8c","tid":2214600,"uid":98899,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-23T12:57:33.000Z","msg":"cap水"}]}